{{> header title="Confirm Account Deletion"}}

<div class="email-body">
  <h1>Confirm Account Deletion</h1>

  <p>Hi {{userName}},</p>

  <p>We received a request to permanently delete your account. This action is
    <strong>irreversible</strong> and will result in:
  </p>

  <ul style="margin: 16px 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #334155;">
    <li>Loss of access to your account and all associated data.</li>
    <li>Deletion of your personal information from our servers.</li>
    <li>Termination of any active subscriptions or services linked to your account.</li>
  </ul>

  <p><strong>If you want to proceed with the account deletion, click the button below:</strong></p>

  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
    <a href="{{confirmationUrl}}" class="button"
      style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626 0%, #b91c1c 100%); box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.3);">
      Confirm Account Deletion
    </a>
  </div>

  <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #64748b;">If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
  <p
    style="word-break: break-all; background-color: #f8fafc; padding: 12px; border-radius: 8px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; color: #0284c7;">
    {{confirmationUrl}}
  </p>

  <div class="subscription-details" style="margin: 24px 0;">
    <h2 style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px;">Security Information:</h2>
    <div class="subscription-list">
      <div class="subscription-row">
        <span class="subscription-label">â€¢ Expires in:</span>
        <span class="subscription-value">{{expiryTime}} hour(s)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="subscription-row">
        <span class="subscription-label">â€¢ Request IP:</span>
        <span class="subscription-value">{{requestIP}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="subscription-row">
        <span class="subscription-label">â€¢ Request Time:</span>
        <span class="subscription-value">{{requestDate}}</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="background-color: #f0f9ff; border: 1px solid #bae6fd; border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px; margin: 24px 0;">
    <strong style="color: #0284c7;">ðŸ’¡ Changed Your Mind?</strong>
    <p style="margin: 8px 0 0 0; color: #0c4a6e; font-size: 14px;">
      If you don't want to delete your account, simply ignore this email. Your account will remain active and
      secure.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h3 style="color: #0284c7; font-size: 18px; margin-top: 32px;">Still Have Questions?</h3>
  <p>If you didn't request account deletion or have concerns about your account security, please contact our support
    team immediately.</p>

  <p>We're sorry to see you go, but we understand that circumstances change.</p>

  <p style="margin-top: 32px;">
    Best regards,<br>
    <strong>The Team</strong>
  </p>
</div>

{{> footer}}